"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"FAUNA:3.21\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">3.21</span> 標題：麻雀、雀鳥（sparrow）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來：צִפּוֹר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯：tsippor)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen7:14\">GEN 7:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:10\">GEN 15:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:4\">LEV 14:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:5\">LEV 14:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:6\">LEV 14:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:6\">LEV 14:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:6\">LEV 14:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:7\">LEV 14:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:49\">LEV 14:49</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:50\">LEV 14:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:51\">LEV 14:51</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:51\">LEV 14:51</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:52\">LEV 14:52</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:52\">LEV 14:52</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:53\">LEV 14:53</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut14:11\">DEU 14:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:6\">DEU 22:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job40:29\">JOB 40:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps11:1\">PSA 11:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps84:4\">PSA 84:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:8\">PSA 102:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:17\">PSA 104:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps124:7\">PSA 124:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:5\">PRO 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:23\">PRO 7:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:2\">PRO 26:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:8\">PRO 27:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:12\">ECC 9:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:4\">ECC 12:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa31:5\">ISA 31:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:52\">LAM 3:52</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:11\">HOS 11:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos3:5\">AMO 3:5</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：στρουθίον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯：strouthion)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:29\">MAT 10:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:31\">MAT 10:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:6\">LUK 12:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:7\">LUK 12:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Tob2:10\">TOB 2:10</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">討論</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p><figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0825_sparrow.jpg\" alt=\"麻雀\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">麻雀 (Pixabay)</figcaption></figure>希臘文<em>strouthion</em> 肯定是指麻雀，然而希伯來文<em>tippor</em> 實際上是一個集合名詞，指與麻雀大小相仿的各種鳥類。人們用網和陷阱捕捉這些小鳥，特別是麻雀，這是窮人飲食的重要組成部分。</p>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p><figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0826_sparrows.jpg\" alt=\"麻雀群\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">麻雀群 (Pixabay)</figcaption></figure>在以色列地有三種常見的麻雀，家麻雀（學名<em>Passer domesticus</em> ）、西班牙麻雀（又稱「黑胸麻雀」；學名<em>Passer hispaniolensis</em> ）和死海麻雀（學名<em>Passer moabiticus</em> ）。這三種都是長著小斑點的棕色鳥。在城鎮和居民點周圍，棲息著許多屬於鵐科、雀科和鶯科的其他小型鳥類。特別地，麻雀通常大群生活，也在一起築巢。所有這些鳥都吃種子，主要是草籽和穀物。</p>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">特殊意義或象徵意義</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>麻雀被視為禮儀上潔淨的鳥類，與窮人關係比較密切。</p>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>世界各地都有麻雀或類似麻雀的小鳥，找到一個當地的對等詞通常並不困難。<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:8\">PSA 102:8</a> （《和》102:7）中提到「房頂上孤單的雀鳥」，如果是指麻雀，這句話就還有言外之意，因為麻雀很少被人單獨看到；這就表明，詩人因為與親朋好友分離而感到孤獨。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
